[{"type":"{{","value":[["pagebanner"],["Pagebanner default.jpg"]]},"\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["File:Oppeln - Altstadt.jpg"],["thumb"],["350px"],["Opole"]]},"\n\n",{"type":"'''","value":[{"type":"[","value":["http:\/\/www.opole.pl\/en Opole"]}]}," is the capital city of ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Opole Voivodeship"]]},", in south west ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Poland"]]},". The historical capital of Upper Silesia was badly damaged during the USSR invasion of Silesia at the end of World War II, but many fine houses in the old town have been rebuilt. The city is known for the one of the most popular song festivals in Poland, which takes place each year in June. It is also home to Poland's small German minority.\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Get in"]},"\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["File:Opole - Wieża Piastowska 01.jpg"],["thumb"],["Piast tower from 13\/14th century"]]},"\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["Image:PL Opole Ratusz.JPG"],["thumb"],["Opole - Town Hall"]]},"\n\n",{"type":"===","value":["By plane"]},"\nInternational airports are located in the nearby cities of ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Katowice"]]}," and ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Wrocław"]]},".\n\n",{"type":"===","value":["By train"]},"\n\nOpole has a very good train connection with ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Wrocław"]]},", ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Katowice"]]}," and ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Krakow"],["Kraków"]]},". There are daily train arrivals from most cities in western and southern Poland. Direct train from ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Warsaw"]]}," arrives 3 times per day. There is also a direct connection with ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Częstochowa"]]},".\n\nAlso note that once a day there's a EuroCity ",{"type":"[","value":["http:\/\/www.intercity.pl\/?page=timetable&ph_center_start=show&tsr_id=1182 \"Wawel\""]}," train from ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Hamburg"]]}," to ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Krakow"],["Kraków"]]},", which stops at Opole Central (Opole Główne) station as well.\n\nSee: ",{"type":"[","value":["http:\/\/www.pkp.pl\/ Polish State Railways"]}," (",{"type":"[","value":["http:\/\/rozklad.pkp.pl\/bin\/query.exe\/pn? route planner"]},")\n\n",{"type":"===","value":["By car"]},"\n\nYou can easily get there by car from ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Katowice"]]}," and ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Wrocław"]]}," by the ",{"type":"'''","value":["A4 Motorway"]},".\n\n",{"type":"===","value":["By bus"]},"\n\nMany international connections (see ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Poland#By bus"],["Poland::By bus"]]},"). There is a big bus company in Opole (",{"type":"[","value":["http:\/\/www.sindbad.pl Sindbad"]},").\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Get around"]},"\nMost important locations can be reached on foot. Public transport may be used for traveling outside the city centre (",{"type":"[","value":["http:\/\/www.mzkopole.pl\/rozklad\/index.html bus timetables"]},"). One-ride ticket costs 2.60 zł, (1.30 zł for students and 1.60 zł for children).\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["See"]},"\n\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"'''","value":["Piast Tower"]}," remain of Piast Castle"]},{"type":"*","value":[" 14th century ",{"type":"'''","value":["Franciscan church"]},", a Piast mausoleum"]},{"type":"*","value":[" 19th century ",{"type":"'''","value":["Town Hall"]}]},{"type":"*","value":[" Eclectic ",{"type":"'''","value":["train station"]}," building"]},"\n",{"type":"===","value":["Museums"]},"\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["File:Muzeum Wsi Opolskiej - chata 01.jpg"],["thumb"],["Museum of Rural Architecture"]]},"\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["see"],["name=Opole Regional Museum"],["alt=Muzeum Śląska Opolskiego"],["url=http:\/\/muzeum.opole.pl\/"],["email="],["address="],["lat="],["long="],["directions="],["phone="],["tollfree="],["fax="],["hours="],["price="],["content=Several branches in three different buildings."]]}]},"\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["see"],["name=Opole Open-Air Museum of Rural Architecture"],["alt=Muzeum Wsi Opolskiej"],["url=http:\/\/www.muzeumwsiopolskiej.pl\/en"],["email="],["address=ul. Wrocławska 174"],["lat="],["long="],["directions="],["phone="],["tollfree="],["fax="],["hours="],["price=10 \/ 5 zł, Mondays free"],["content="]]}]},"\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["see"],["name=Modern Art Gallery"],["alt=Galeria Sztuki Współczesnej"],["url=http:\/\/www.galeriaopole.pl\/en"],["email="],["address=pl. Teatralny 12"],["lat="],["long="],["directions="],["phone="],["tollfree="],["fax="],["hours="],["price="],["content="]]}]},"\n",{"type":"==","value":["Do"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Buy"]},"\n\nThere are several shopping centres, one of them is ",{"type":"'''","value":[{"type":"[","value":["http:\/\/www.solariscenter.pl\/ Solaris Center"]}]},".\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Eat"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Drink"]},"\nNear the Town Hall is a British-styled bar (pub) named the ",{"type":"'''","value":["John Bull Pub"]},". It is primarily indoors but during warmer months -or if a live band or DJ is performing - it is not uncommon for the outside beer garden to be open. The inside of the pub is decorated in the English or British-style (dark wood, pictures of British customs and landmarks, etc.). It is furnished with numerous televisions which are normally tuned to any number of football (soccer) matches. The bar, like most in Poland, only serves a few brands of draught beer (piwo) rather than a typical American bar that can have dozens of beers on tap. All types of domestic and international liquor are available.\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Sleep"]},"\n",{"type":"===","value":["Splurge"]},"\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["sleep"],["name=Hotel Mercure"],["url=http:\/\/www.orbis.pl\/en\/opole\/hotels\/mercure_opole"],["email=mer.opole@orbis.pl"],["address=ul. Krakowska 57-59"],["lat="],["long="],["directions="],["phone=+48 (0)77 451 81 00"],["tollfree="],["fax=+48 (0)77 451 81 99"],["hours="],["price="],["checkin="],["checkout="],["content=Central location, near the rail and bus stations."]]}," "]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["sleep"],["name=Hotel Festival"],["alt="],["url=http:\/\/www.festival.com.pl\/"],["email="],["address=ul. Oleska 86"],["lat="],["long="],["directions="],["phone="],["tollfree="],["fax="],["checkin="],["checkout="],["price="],["content="]]}]},"\n",{"type":"==","value":["Go next"]},"\n\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["IsPartOf"],["Opole Voivodeship"]]},"\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["outlinecity"]]},"\n\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["Wikipedia:Opole"]]},"\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["geo"],["50.666666666667"],["17.933333333333"]]}]